    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine Domini nostri Iehsu Christi Dei eterni, anno ab incarnatione
                        eius millesimo centesimo sexagesimo primo, septimo idus ianuarii, indictione
                        nona. Manifestus sum ego <persName><name ref="Paganus"
                            >Paganellus</name></persName> filius quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Rodelandus">Rolandi</name></persName> quia per hanc cartulam
                        vendo et trado tibi <persName><name ref="Wido">Guido</name></persName>,
                        divino nomine Dei gratia rectori <orgName key="#Hospitals"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs key="#Hospitals">ospitalis</rs> Dei et
                            Sancti Gilii et Sancti Iacobi</orgName> de <placeName key="#Hospitals"
                            ref="#places/3207">Altepascio</placeName>, ad opus et utilitatem
                        predicte ecclesie et ospitalis et pro anime mee remedio ac salute, tibi Deo
                        et predicte et ecclesie et ospitali offero idest unam petiam de terra mea
                        que est campus, in locis et finibus de <placeName key="#Forests"
                            ref="#places/3241">Porcari et ubi dicitur Bosco <persName><name
                                    ref="Martinus Corti">Martini
                        Corti</name></persName></placeName>. Et tene uno capo in carraia et alio
                        capo tene in terra et prato meo. Latus unum in terra <persName><name
                                ref="Mancio">Mansi</name></persName> quondam *** et alio lato in
                        terra que dicitur <rs key="#Forests">Bosco</rs> suprascripti Martini Corti.
                        (…) <foreign>Dimensioni</foreign>: cultra una et sextariorum duo.
                            <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: sol. centum viginti bonorum denariorum.
                            <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum (…) et insuper penam argenti optimi
                        libras decem. (…) Actum <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/3242"
                            >Putheuli</placeName> prope <orgName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3222"><rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                            Sancti Petri</orgName>. (…) Signum manus <persName
                            key="#Witness #Gastaldus/vicegastaldus"><name ref="Errigettus"
                                >Errigeti</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">castaldii</rs> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Arnulfus">Arnolfi</name></persName> et <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Septus">Septi</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Roselmus">Rosselmi</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Ianni">Ianni</name></persName> (…)
                                <persName><name ref="Rainuccius">Rainucini</name></persName>
                        rogatorum <rs key="#Witness">testium</rs>. (S) <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Gandulfus">Glandulfus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notarius</rs> domni regis post traditam complevi
                        et dedi.</ab>
